## Decisions Needed

{% if archetype == 'standup' %}
- Confirm today's priority for each participant
- Identify anyone needing help
{% elif archetype == 'retro' %}
- Agree on top 3 things to change next sprint
- Vote on action items
{% elif archetype == 'sprint-review' %}
- Demo sign-off per completed item
- Accept/reject scope changes
{% elif archetype == 'planning' %}
- Confirm sprint capacity
- Commit to sprint backlog
{% else %}
- Confirm week priorities and tradeoffs
- Confirm escalation path for blockers
- Align on cross-team dependencies
{% endif %}

